				<description>&lt;p&gt;It’s so easy to do. Just define in front matter an image and a pattern image. Instead of a pattern you can also use a color. Have a look at the &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/feeling-responsive/design/header-image-color/&quot;&gt;example with a background color&lt;/a&gt;.
